  ('optometrist-moex-00114', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位驗光師對病人進行視網膜檢影法（retinoscopy），此位驗光師的工作距離是50cm。發現分別以0.00D 鏡片沿軸度120度達到中和點，+2.00D鏡片沿軸度30度達到中和點。則這位病人的度數為何？', '["+2.00DS/-2.00DC×120", "+1.50DS/-2.00DC×120", "+0.50DS/-2.00DC×030", "+planoDS/-2.00DC×030"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "99730c6ed7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "273f9b848536", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00115', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '使用角膜弧度儀測量角膜弧度後得到下列資訊：42.50@180/43.50@090,MCAR，請問關於此資訊的敘述何 者錯誤？', '["角膜在180度位置度數為42.50D；在090度位置度數為43.50D", "角膜散光為-1.00×180", "角膜為逆規散光", "MCAR代表影像清楚且規則"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "99730c6ed7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "273f9b848536", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00116', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-114-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於靜態檢影鏡（staticretinoscopy）的敘述何者不適當？', '["確認受測者眼睛他覺式遠距離屈光狀態及調節狀態", "檢查結果可作為自覺式驗光的起始點", "當受測者無法配合自覺式驗光時檢查結果可當作最終處方", "可配合綜合驗光儀、板鏡或試片組等進行檢查"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "99730c6ed7d9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "273f9b848536", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
